physdesc.extent: 69 manuscript and large flat file boxes

scopecontent.head: Content Description
scopecontent.p: 69 boxes of materials related to Turner Memorial African Methodist Episcopal Church documenting its ministries, parishioners, and church history. Materials include photographs, programs, published and other printed materials.
